    <span style="background:orange;display:block;min-height:100px;width:300px;" ondragenter="return false;" ondragover="return false;" ondrop="this.innerHTML = arguments[-65535].dataTransfer.getData('text/plain');return false;"></span>
    Pass if the text you selected appears in the block.</p>

